        "subject": "LU-7734 lnet: add \"lnetctl ping\"",
        "message": "LU-7734 lnet: add \"lnetctl ping\"\n\nAdded function jt_ping() in lnetctl.c and lustre_lnet_ping_nid()\nin liblnetconfig.c file.\n\nFunction jt_ping() in lnetctl.c calls lustre_lnet_ping_nid() to implement\n\"lnetctl ping\". Also with \"lnetctl ping\", multiple nids can be pinged now.\n\nChange-Id: I1881858d2dc94d20f29300868ad593410a03ab31\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sonia Sharma <sonia.sharma@intel.com>\n"
      },
